{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/6-spin-off-anime-yang-keren/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"6 Spin-off Anime Yang Sama Keren Dengan Anime Utamanya","content":"<p>Di dunia hiburan seperti komik, film atau animasi ada yang dinamakan sebagai <em>“spin-off”</em>. Apa itu <em>spin-off</em>? Secara sederhana, sebuah <em>spin-off</em> adalah ‘sempalan’. Sebuah percabangan dari sesuatu yang utama. <em>Spin-off</em> bisa dikategorikan sebagai bagian dari yang utama namun normalnya tidak memiliki nilai setinggi bagian utama.</p>\n<p>Tunggu dulu. Jadi <em>spin-off</em> tidak penting? Jawabannya adalah ‘tidak juga’.</p>\n<p>Walaupun dikatakan tidak bernilai setinggi bagian utama namun sebuah <em>spin-off</em> seringkali memiliki peranan penting dalam hal ekspansi cerita. Contoh mudah dari situasi ini adalah <em>spin-off</em> trilogi film “The Mummy” berjudul “The Scorpion King” (2002) yang dibintangi oleh mantan pegulat professional Dwayne “The Rock” Johnson. Film The Scorpion King mengulas soal karakter Mathayus sebelum menjadi Scorpion King. Dalam <em>timeline</em> trilogi The Mummy film ini berada sebelum “The Mummy Returns” (2001).</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_50936\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-50936\" data-attachment-id=\"50936\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/6-spin-off-anime-yang-keren/attachment/01-spin-off-anime/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/01-spin-off-anime.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-spin-off-anime\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/01-spin-off-anime-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/01-spin-off-anime.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-50936\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/01-spin-off-anime.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: YouTube\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/01-spin-off-anime.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/01-spin-off-anime-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-50936\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: YouTube</p></div></p>\n<p>Atau lihat juga dua film <em>spin-off</em> “Star Wars” saga yang sudah beredar, yaitu “Rogue One” (2016) dan “<a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/review-solo-a-star-wars-story/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Solo</a>” (2018).</p>\n<p>Keduanya merupakan <em>spin-off</em> yang memiliki plot serta <em>timeline</em> sebelum “A New Hope / Episode IV”. Rogue One dan Solo bukanlah bagian inti dari Star Wars. Hanya <em>spin-off</em>. Namun punya peran penting dalam ekspansi kisah Star Wars itu sendiri.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_50937\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-50937\" data-attachment-id=\"50937\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/6-spin-off-anime-yang-keren/attachment/02-spin-off-anime/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/02-spin-off-anime.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-spin-off-anime\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/02-spin-off-anime-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/02-spin-off-anime.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-50937\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/02-spin-off-anime.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: SquareSpace\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/02-spin-off-anime.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/02-spin-off-anime-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-50937\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: SquareSpace</p></div></p>\n<p>Tapi apakah semua <em>spin-off</em> penting dan harus dibuat?</p>\n<p>Tidak. Terkadang sebuah <em>spin-off</em> justru membuat jidat mengkerut karena tidak punya makna. Atau penyampaiannya berkualitas buruk. Contoh kasus: film “Evan Almighty” (2007) yang merupakan <em>spin-off</em> dari film komedi sukses Jim Carrey “Bruce Almighty” (2003). Bruce Almighty dikemas dengan konsep menarik sementara Evan Almighty sebaliknya.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_50938\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-50938\" data-attachment-id=\"50938\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/6-spin-off-anime-yang-keren/attachment/03-spin-off-anime/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/03-spin-off-anime.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-spin-off-anime\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/03-spin-off-anime-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/03-spin-off-anime.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-50938\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/03-spin-off-anime.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: NumeroUnity\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/03-spin-off-anime.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/03-spin-off-anime-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-50938\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: NumeroUnity</p></div></p>\n<p>Gimana dengan anime? Apa ada anime <em>spin-off</em> dari sebuah judul anime utama?</p>\n<p>Tentu saja ada! Anime tidak berbeda dari medium gambar bergerak seperti film <em>live action</em>. Mereka punya cerita/kisah yang dapat di “lebarkan” melalui sebuah <em>spin-off</em>. Tujuannya jelas untuk lebih membuat judul utama semakin bernilai. Semakin memiliki plot yang menarik. Dan tentu saja untuk meraup pendapatan yang lebih banyak lagi.</p>\n<p>Dan seperti halnya di film <em>live action</em>, sebuah <em>spin-off</em> anime bisa berakhir sebagai sebuah karya bagus serta menghibur, atau malah sebaliknya.</p>\n<h2>6 Spin-off Anime yang Sekeren Anime Utamanya</h2>\n<h3><strong>1. Full Metal Panic? Fumoffu</strong></h3>\n<p><strong>Spin-off Anime: Full Metal Panic!</strong></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_50939\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-50939\" data-attachment-id=\"50939\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/6-spin-off-anime-yang-keren/attachment/04-spin-off-anime/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/04-spin-off-anime.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-spin-off-anime\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/04-spin-off-anime-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/04-spin-off-anime.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-50939\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/04-spin-off-anime.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: Funimation\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/04-spin-off-anime.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/04-spin-off-anime-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-50939\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Funimation</p></div></p>\n<p><em>List</em> ini memang disusun secara <em>random</em> namun buat saya “Full Metal Panic? Fumoffu” ada di posisi tinggi dari anime <em>spin-off</em> favorit. Memiliki <em>tone</em> yang berbeda dari serial aslinya, Fumoffu lebih konsen di bagian komedi dan <em>‘high school romansu’</em> antara dua karakter utama Full Metal Panic: Sagara Sousuke dan Kaname Chidori. Tidak ada perang robot, tidak ada drama politik, hanya kisah keseharian anak-anak SMA di Jepang.</p>\n<p>Dan Bonta-kun. Ini soal Bonta-kun. Maksud saya, siapa yang tidak pengen punya Bonta-kun??</p>\n<p><strong>Baca Juga: <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/anime-spring-2018-baru/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Butuh Tontonan Baru? Coba 10 Anime Baru Musim Semi 2018 Ini!</a></strong></p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/rYHyGKZdw2o\" width=\"722\" height=\"406\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<h3><strong>2. Fate/kaleid liner Prisma Illya</strong></h3>\n<p><strong>Spin-off Anime: Fate series</strong></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_50940\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-50940\" data-attachment-id=\"50940\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/6-spin-off-anime-yang-keren/attachment/05-spin-off-anime/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/05-spin-off-anime.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05-spin-off-anime\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/05-spin-off-anime-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/05-spin-off-anime.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-50940\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/05-spin-off-anime.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber gambar: Laku-Cinema\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/05-spin-off-anime.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/05-spin-off-anime-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-50940\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber gambar: Laku-Cinema</p></div></p>\n<p>Tanpa <em>spin-off</em> saja, serial “Fate” sudah terasa sangat njelimet membingungkan untuk di ikutin. Sistem <em>magic</em> yang kompleks, <em>timeline</em> yang penuh alternatif, cukup untuk bikin mereka yang pertama memasuki <em>franchise</em> ini kebingungan. Prisma Illya adalah salah satu dari banyak <em>spin-off</em> serial Fate dan dikemas dalam model <em>cute</em> serta <em>fuwa-fuwa-fluffy</em> seperti serial-serial mahou shojo. Namun berhubung ini adalah bagian dari Fate series, siap-siap saja dengan kompleksitas dalam cerita/plot walau penampilannya <em>kawaii</em>.</p>\n<p><strong>Baca Juga: <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/fate-series-dari-game-pc-hingga-meraih-popularitas-di-smartphone/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Fate Series: Dari Game PC Hingga Meraih Popularitas Di Smartphone</a></strong></p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/5Q-WXlcMIQc\" width=\"722\" height=\"406\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<h3><strong>3. Soul Eater Not!</strong></h3>\n<p><strong>Spin-off Anime: Soul Eater</strong></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_50941\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-50941\" data-attachment-id=\"50941\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/6-spin-off-anime-yang-keren/attachment/06-spin-off-anime/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/06-spin-off-anime.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"06-spin-off-anime\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/06-spin-off-anime-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/06-spin-off-anime.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-50941\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/06-spin-off-anime.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: Comixology\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/06-spin-off-anime.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/06-spin-off-anime-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-50941\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Comixology</p></div></p>\n<p>Ingat anime Soul Eater dong? Keren ‘kan? Banyak yang suka dengan anime itu. Tema yang unik dengan deretan karakter berdesain nyentrik. Sayangnya untuk mayoritas fans (setidaknya seperti yang terlihat di internet), <em>spin-off</em> Soul Eater berjudul “Soul Eater Not!” dinilai tidak sebagus serial aslinya. Mengambil <em>timeline</em> sebelum kisah asli Soul Eater dimulai, karakter yang jadi pemeran utama juga berbeda dari cerita utama. Sebagai <em>prequel</em> cerita Soul Eater, Soul Eater Not! sebenarnya oke-oke saja menurut saya. Tidak buruk, tapi tidak pula punya pencapaian Soul Eater sebelumnya.</p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Z8HSMFelQIU\" width=\"722\" height=\"406\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<h3><strong>4. The Disappearance of Nagato Yuki-chan</strong></h3>\n<p><strong>Spin-off Anime: The Disappearance of Suzumiya Haruhi</strong></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_50942\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-50942\" data-attachment-id=\"50942\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/6-spin-off-anime-yang-keren/attachment/07-spin-off-anime/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/07-spin-off-anime.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"07-spin-off-anime\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/07-spin-off-anime-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/07-spin-off-anime.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-50942\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/07-spin-off-anime.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: Funimation\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/07-spin-off-anime.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/07-spin-off-anime-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-50942\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Funimation</p></div></p>\n<p>Untuk banyak fans berat anime, nama “Suzumiya Haruhi” tentu bukanlah nama yang asing lagi. <em>Light novel</em> dan anime Haruhi sukses dan digemari. The Disappearance of Nagato Yuki-chan sendiri adalah kisah <em>spin-off</em> dari Haruhi Suzumiya. Dengan tokoh utama ‘versi manusia’ dari Nagato Yuki-chan dan berada di <em>alternate universe</em> masa Haruhi Suzumiya, kisah The Disappearance of Nagato Yuki-chan di desain dengan lembut dan kalem. Sesuai dengan karakteristik Nagato Yuki-chan itu sendiri. Sebagai <em>spin-off</em> dari kisah Haruhi Suzumiya, Nagato Yuki-chan termasuk keren dan menarik. Tapi ya jangan harapkan keriuhan ala Haruhi Suzumiya disini ya!</p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/rqOjj0N6OZA\" width=\"722\" height=\"406\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<h3><strong>5. The King of Braves GaoGaiGar</strong></h3>\n<p><strong>Spin-off Anime: Brave series</strong></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_50943\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-50943\" data-attachment-id=\"50943\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/6-spin-off-anime-yang-keren/attachment/08-spin-off-anime/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/08-spin-off-anime.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"08-spin-off-anime\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/08-spin-off-anime-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/08-spin-off-anime.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-50943\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/08-spin-off-anime.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: Crunchyroll\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/08-spin-off-anime.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/08-spin-off-anime-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-50943\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Crunchyroll</p></div></p>\n<p>Anime bertema “Super Robot” sudah biasa memiliki berbagai <em>spin-off</em>. Misalnya saja serial “Mazinger” dari <em>maestro</em> Super Robot Jepang, Go Nagai, yang punya sederet <em>spin-off</em>. Yuusha Ou Gaogaiga sendiri merupakan <em>spin-off</em> #8 (alias terakhir) dari serial robot GaoGaiGar. Sebagai bagian dari <em>genre</em> Super Robot, GaoGaiGar mengusung hal-hal dan elemen-elemen klasik Super Robot yang keren! Terutama untuk anak-anak cowok yang biasa menggemari hal-hal berbau robot dan <em>gattai/henshin</em> ala Jepang.</p>\n<p><strong>Baca Juga: <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/go-nagai-mangaka-senior-yang-mempopulerkan-genre-ecchi-dan-super-robot/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Go Nagai: Mangaka Senior yang Mempopulerkan Genre Ecchi dan Super Robot</a></strong></p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/zgAazreoQqA\" width=\"722\" height=\"406\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<h3><strong>6. Dragon Ball Z: The History of Trunks</strong></h3>\n<p><strong>Spin-off Anime: Dragon Ball Z</strong></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_50944\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-50944\" data-attachment-id=\"50944\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/6-spin-off-anime-yang-keren/attachment/09-spin-off-anime/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/09-spin-off-anime.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"09-spin-off-anime\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/09-spin-off-anime-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/09-spin-off-anime.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-50944\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/09-spin-off-anime.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: YouTube\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/09-spin-off-anime.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/09-spin-off-anime-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-50944\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: YouTube</p></div></p>\n<p>Ini adalah satu dari banyaknya <em>spin-off</em> Dragon Ball series di luar sana. Dan menurut saya yang paling dramatis dan menyedihkan. Berada di <em>timeline</em> <em>‘what-if’</em> atau ‘gimana kalau seluruh jagoan Dragon Ball Z mati di tangan Android 17 &amp; 18 serta menyisakan seorang Trunks untuk berjuang menyelamatkan dunia’, anime OVA The History of Trunks memiliki animasi yang bagus serta plot yang menyayat hati. Kita juga akan menyaksikan kelahiran “Super Saiyan Trunks” disini. Sebuah <em>spin-off</em> yang sangat perlu untuk ditonton oleh fans Dragon Ball secara umum.</p>\n<p><strong>Baca Juga: <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/dragon-ball-super-broly-saiyan-legendaris/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Dragon Ball Super: Broly Tampilkan Super Saiyan Legendaris!</a></strong></p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/43HmSc1Z-sM\" width=\"541\" height=\"406\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<hr />\n<p>Sebuah <em>spin-off</em> tidak akan pernah berhenti di produksi. Dan sebuah <em>spin-off</em>, secara teori, bisa saja melebihi pencapaian serial aslinya. Semua tergantung kehebatan para tokoh di belakang pembuatannya. Dan penerimaan dari fans serial asli asal <em>spin-off</em> itu sendiri.</p>\n<p>Apa kamu tidak setuju dengan daftar <em>spin-off</em> ini? Punya <em>list</em> sendiri? Suarakan pendapatmu!</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/comic\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img data-attachment-id=\"50176\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/manga-terpopuler-di-indonesia-pada-2018/attachment/print-7/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Banner-Home-CIAYO-Comics.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1534766427&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Print&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Banner Halaman CIAYO Comics id\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Banner-Home-CIAYO-Comics-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Banner-Home-CIAYO-Comics.jpg\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-50176\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Banner-Home-CIAYO-Comics.jpg\" alt=\"Baca komik online di CIAYO Comics\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Banner-Home-